snippet.title: Helium Rain - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Helium Rain is a realistic space opera for PC. Get it on Steam :  https://store.steampowered.com/app/681330/Helium_Rain/

After one year in Early Access and hundreds of bugs fixed, we're releasing the full game !
